'''Dominic Karl Roque''' (born July 20, 1990) is a [[Filipino people|Filipino]] [[actor]] and [[Model (person)|model]]. He is known to his role in [[Aryana]] and [[May Isang Pangarap]]. He is under management of [[ABS-CBN]]<U+2019>s [[Star Magic]] talents.<ref name=imdb>IMDb (2013)[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm5063596/ ''Dominic Roque Actor Filmography''] Retrieved 1 2013</ref>

==Background==
Dominic Roque was born and raised in the province of [[Cavite]]. He is the son of businessman and a company president. He is also a nephew of known actress [[Beth Tamayo]].<ref>akulits Lambingan <U+00A9> (2013) [http://makulits.com/dominique-roque/ ''Dominique Roque Biography Profile and Pictures''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref> He attended college in [[De La Salle<U+2013>College of Saint Benilde]] and took Tourism course.<ref>GeoTayo Phils (2012)[http://www.geotayo.com/dominickarl_roque.php ''Dominic Roque Bio''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref>

==Career==
Roque began modeling and endorsing several companies before headed into acting. He was a model for Cosmopolitan talents since 2008, where he modeled the Philippine clothing brand, [[Penshoppe]].

In 2010, Roque debuted onscreen in the soap opera casting [[Habang May Buhay]] playing Mark. He later took his first major role in the fantasy-drama series, [[Aryana]] in 2012.<ref name=imdb /> He played the character Hubert, wherein he co-starred and paired to [[Ella Cruz]].

While taping the series as career breakthrough, he did several guesting roles including [[Bandila]]<ref>Bulletin Solutions, Inc PinoyExchange (2012)[http://www.pinoyexchange.com/forums/showthread.php?t=573004&page=3 ''Dominic in Bandila''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref> and in the morning talk show [[Kris TV]] in which he issued in relating to [[Kathryn Bernardo]].<ref name=imdb /><ref>ABS-CBN Interactive (2012)[http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/entertainment/10/12/12/aryana-actor-meets-crush-kathryn-bernardo ''"Aryana" actor meets "crush" Kathryn Bernardo'' ] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref><ref>PEP.ph Philippine Entertainment Portal Inc. (2013)[http://www.pep.ph/celeb/fashion-and-beauty/health-and-beauty/28540/good-health-means-no-alcohol-for-dominic-roque ''Good health means no alcohol for Dominic Roque ''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref>

Subsequently, after ended up the [[Aryana]] in January 2013, he signed his second major role in the noontime drama series [[May Isang Pangarap]] played as an arrogant Alvin.<ref name=imdb /><ref name=push>Push.com ABS-CBN Interactive (2013)[http://push.abs-cbn.com/features/8769/dominic-roque-reveals-he-has-a-new-show-and-a-new-love-team-partner/ ''Dominic Roque reveals he has a new show and a new love team partner''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref> He paired with [[Erin Ocampo]] who also a newbie actress.<ref name=push />

In June 2013, Roque had his movie debut in the film [[Pagpag (2013 film)|Pagpag]], an [[MMFF]] entry for 2013. He co-starred with [[Daniel Padilla]] and [[Kathryn Bernardo]].<ref>mynoytech (2013)[http://www.mynoytech.com/2013/06/pagpag-starring-daniel-padilla-and.html ''"Pagpag" Starring Daniel Padilla and Kathryn Bernardo(MMFF 2013 Entry) ''] Retrieved July 1, 2013</ref>

